      "updated": 1777018623069,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "n = 7\n\n\n1 -> 1\n2 -> 1 2\n3 -> 1 3\n4 -> 1 2 4\n5 -> 1 5\n6 -> 1 2 3 6\n7 -> 1 7",
